{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aa4bdc8c4e","title":"给《人民日报》社编辑的信","origin":"牛汉、邓小平主编《六月雪》(经济日报出版社，1998)。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13478f6e2b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":9,"articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"},{"id":"661b2c3cb0","name":"葛佩琦"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"555cee5ed6","type":"title","text":"给《人民日报》社编辑的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"2b0e0838f7","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学葛佩琦","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"8f01e27b83","type":"subtitle","text":"(葛佩琦：中国人民大学工业经济系讲师)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"c4e09c3ceb","type":"paragraph","text":"编辑同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"714e9e4f39","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日你报七版刊登的我的那个发言，有些地方和原意有出入，请予更正。“我要重述一遍……只空喊万岁是没有用的”这段报道的全文是：“我要重述一遍，群众总要推翻共产党，杀共产党人。若你们再不改，不争口气，那必是这条道路，总有这么一天。这也是合乎社会主义发展规律的，只空喊万岁是没有用的。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"0b2b7387ef","type":"paragraph","text":"应改为","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"2cdb52bb93","type":"paragraph","text":"“在这次整风中，如果党内同志不积极改正缺点，继续争取群众的信任，那不仅可以自趋灭亡，而且发展下去，可以危及党的生存。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"},{"id":"48ef65f6f6","type":"paragraph","text":" 葛佩琦1957年6月9日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e"}],"page":{"id":"1a18dc8303","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aa4bdc8c4e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}